               stealing a blue silk coat embroidered with gold, value 40 s. a blue silk waistcoat embroidered with gold, value 20 s. a pair of blue silk breeches, with gold buttons and garters, value 15 s. and a tissue and gold waistcoat, value 40 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17780115-2-person56">
                        Edwin
                         Lascelles
                     <interp inst="t17780115-2-person56" type="surname" value="Lascelles"></interp>
